authConnectionFailedWsDetail:
Unable to connect to VNC server because the <b>WebSocket upgrade request was rejected (400)</b>.<br><br>If you are using Nginx or another proxy, this is likely due to <b>missing Upgrade header configuration</b>.<br>Please ensure your proxy config includes:<br><pre style='text-align:left;background:#f5f7fa;padding:8px;border-radius:4px;font-size:12px;overflow-x:auto'>proxy_http_version 1.1;
proxy_set_header Upgrade $http_upgrade;
proxy_set_header Connection "upgrade";</pre>
